title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H1 – Jun 13 2022

description:
Dems abandon Biden ship, push Trump prosecution. AOC won't say if she'll back Biden in 2024. YouTube star Jake Paul tweets against Biden. Larry Summers says a recession is coming. Biden killed your 401(k). Would AG Merrick Garland really file charges against Trump? NYC to require masks at public pools. Buck gets stuck at the airport.
